       	   O creature of lard!
	d: What?
	   No/nBonzo?换行
	e: 2 + 2 = 4 
6. 
	c语言的关键字：
	与数据类型有关的：void, short, int, long, float, double, unsigned, void, enum, struct, typedef, union, sizeof, _Bool, _Complex, _Imaginary
	与寄存器有关的：  auto, volatile, register, restrict
	与访问权限有关的：extern, static,inline, const
	与流程控制有关的：if, else, while, do, for, break, continue, goto, switch, case, default
	特殊的：	  return
	-------------------------
	显然题目中是关键字的是：int, char 

